\id PHM - Ashéninka, Ucayali-Yurúa NT -Peru 2000 (DBL -2013) 
\h FILEMÓN 
\toc1 Rosankenare Pablo Rotyaantziniri Filemón 
\toc2 Filemón 
\toc3 Flm. 
\mt1 ROSANKENARE PABLO ROTYAANTZINIRI FILEMÓN 
\c 1  
\s1 Wethataantsi 
\p  
\v 1 Naaka Pablo osankenatzimirori jiroka. Tema romonkyaawentaitakenari naaka Jesucristo jaka. Iri notsipatakari iyeki Timoteo nosankenatzimiro jiroka. Eerokatake notyaantzini, Filemón, netakotanewo nowimi, eeroka amitakotapiintanari.  
\v 2 Iro nosankenatzini Apia noshiyakaakeri “choini”, nosankenatziniri eejatzi Arquipo tsipatakairi añaashintsiyetaga. Irijatzi nosankenatzini kemisantzinkaripaini ikaatzi apatotapiintachari pipankoki.  
\v 3 Onkamintha ineshironkataimi Ashitairi Pawa, eejatzi Awinkatharite Jesucristo, kameetha risaikakaayetaimi. 
\s1 Retakonka eejatzi roshirenka Filemón 
\p  
\v 4 Arika namanakoyetemi, antawoite niwetharyaari Pawa.  
\v 5 Tema nokemakotakemi etakotanewo pinatzi, kinatane powiri Awinkatharite Jesús, ari pikantziriri eejatzi ikaatzi rashiyetaari irirori.  
\v 6 Iro namanakotantzimiri onkene paapatziyawakaanaiya eerokapaini pikemisantanaira, pinkemathatanairo kameetha rantakaashiretaimiri Cristo Jesús pikemisantairira.  
\v 7 Iyekí, etako powanairi eeroka kemisantanaatsiri, iroowa iñaantakawori iriroripaini ithaamentaperota. Irojatzi oimoshirenkanari eejatzi naaka, thaamenta nokanta. 
\s1 Pablo ikantakowentziri Onésimo 
\p  
\v 8 Niyotzi, naaka rowake Cristo nantakaimiro onkaate pantairi.  
\v 9 Apatziro nonkowakotemi eepichokiini, tema niyotake tsika pikanta petakotanta. Pablo ninatzi naaka, antarikitapaakena, romonkyaawentaitakenari Jesucristo.  
\v 10 Jirika Onésimo nokowake paakameethamatsitairi. Iriitake noshiyakaakeri naaka iriime notomi, tema naakatake oshiretakaakari Cristo romonkyagaitakenaga. \f + \fr 1:10 \ft Jiroka wairontsi Onésimo riñaaneki iriroripaini oshiyawaitawo akantziri aaka: Pantariri.\f* 
\v 11 Tema te ompantawetyaari jirika, irooma iroñaaka ari impantzimotaimi eeroka, ari inkemetzimotaina naaka eejatzi.  
\v 12 Tema noipiyaimiri Onésimo, netakoneentari.  
\v 13 Osheki nokowawetaka intsipatename. Iri poyaatemineme eeroka ramitakoyetena jaka romonkyagaitakenaga okantakaantziro nokenkithatakotziro Kameethari Ñaantsi.  
\v 14 Iro kameethatatsi, te nokemi pinkantena eeroka oita pikowiri, te nokowi naaka notsiwakakaimiro pantero jiroka, iro nokowake eerokatakera kantatsine oitarika pikowiri panteri. 
\p  
\v 15 Aamaashitya iro rishinetantaitakariri Onésimo rishiyapithatantakemiri pairani, ari onkantya inkemisantantaiyaariri Cristo ripiyantaiyaari intsipatapaimi.  
\v 16 Iro kantacha, te apatziro poshiyakagairi pimperatanewo pikantawetari pairani, poshiyakagairi iriime pirentzi petakoperotanewo. Eejatzi nonkantairi naaka. Eeroka maperotairone petakotaiyaari pimperatari koñaawoini, irijatzi rimperatari eejatzi Awinkatharite.  
\v 17 Tema poshiyakaakena eeroka, naaka pitsipatanewo, ari pinkantairiri eejatzi Onésimo paakameethateri, poshiyakayeri naakame paakameethatzi.  
\v 18 Tzimatsirika iyenakaashitane kaari rinimotakaimi, rireewetzimirika eejatzi, poshiyakayenawo naakame ireewetemine.  
\v 19 Naaka, Pablo osankenatzirori jiroka. Imaperotatya, aritake nipinataimiro rireewetzimiri. Iro kantacha eerokaga ireeweperotakenari naaka nowawisaakoshiretaimira.  
\v 20 Ari okanta iyekí. Nokowataike iriira kantakayaawone Awinkatharite paakameethatairi Onésimo, tema iro kimoshiretakagaanari. \f + \fr 1:20 \ft Kantakotachari jaka “paakameethatairi Onésimo,” ikantatzi: Nokowataike pipantzimotaina eeroka. Tema riñaaneki iriroripaini iwairo inatzi Onésimo jiroka \ft Pantariri. \f* 
\v 21 Iro nosankenatantzimirori jiroka niyotzi ari pimatakenawo, tema pimatapiintakerowa ari panaakaanakero okaatzi nokowakotakemiri.  
\v 22 Nokowake eejatzi, paamagaina niyaatashitemi pisaikira eeroka, ari nimayimotapaakemi. Iroorika pinkowakotanteri pamanakotena, ari rishinetakero Pawa imatya. 
\s1 Weyaantawori riwethatanta eejatzi ritasonkawentantzi 
\p  
\v 23 Riwethatzimi Epafras, notsipatakari jaka romonkyaawentaitanarira Cristo Jesús.  
\v 24 Riwethatzimi eejatzi Marcos, Aristarco, Demas, Lucas, iriitake notsipatapiintakari jaka.  
\v 25 ¡Onkamintha ineshironkataimi Awinkatharite Jesucristo! Ari onkantaitatyeeyaani.